Short:    Motorola Freeware 68xx cross assemblers
Uploader: salamon@gol.com (David Salamon)
Author:   Motorola, Terry E. Rogers, T.Grover, and others
Type:     dev/cross

These are the complete set of Motorola Freeware cross assemblers, as posted
on the Freeware BBS some years ago (and no longer available).  The assemblers
cover the 6800, 6801, 6804, 6805, 6809, and 6811 microprocessors and micro-
controllers.  This is version TER_2.0, and no source code is provided.

